{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"幸容","listener":null,"text":"扬一益二，若论全国贸易，始终是我们的扬州居首，否则我们竹花帮就不能成为南方巴陵帮外的另一大帮。所以在兜兜转转之后，始终都要把总舵迁回这，邵令周这么卖李子通的账，自有其前因后果。","tone":"无奈","chapter":251,"line_start":15,"line_end":19},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"桂锡良","listener":null,"text":"这年多来一直是打打停停，江都三面临江海，港口深阔，要围城谈何容易？兼且李子通在另一大城钟离置有重兵，不时从水道来偷袭围城的敌人，所以杜伏威和沈纶每次于轮番攻城后，都要退军重整生息，好恢复元气，否则李子通怎能捱到今天？","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":55,"line_end":59},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"洛其飞","listener":null,"text":"看来会有点小麻烦。","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":73,"line_end":73},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"只好随机应变。","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":75,"line_end":75},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"骆奉","listener":null,"text":"大王有令，所有抵江都的船只，都要彻查人货，验证无误后，始可入城。","tone":"无奈","chapter":251,"line_start":77,"line_end":79},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"桂锡良","listener":null,"text":"连我们竹花帮的人都不能例外，我今趟可是为大王办事哩！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":251,"line_start":81,"line_end":83},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"骆奉","listener":null,"text":"忍耐点！大家心知肚明内是甚么一回事就成。","tone":"沉声","chapter":251,"line_start":85,"line_end":87},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"骆奉","listener":null,"text":"这些贵客是否来自少帅军的兄弟。","tone":"疑问","chapter":251,"line_start":89,"line_end":91},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"小弟山东'风刀'凌封，见过骆堂主，此行正是奉少帅之命，听候桂堂主差遣。","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":93,"line_end":95},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"骆奉","listener":null,"text":"查验入货的事合情合理，该不是有人故意刁难，望凌兄谅察，否则如何与少帅合作。","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":97,"line_end":99},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"幸容","listener":null,"text":"玉玲夫人重开天香楼，现在已成了扬州最有名的青楼，天香双绝更是南方最有名的两位才女。","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":115,"line_end":117},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"幸容","listener":null,"text":"骆堂主对我们算是最好的了！只有他肯帮我们说两句话。","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":133,"line_end":136},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"那沈北昌呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":251,"line_start":137,"line_end":137},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"幸容","listener":null,"text":"沈老头很阴沉，谁都不知他真正想的是甚么，我看邵令周对他很有顾忌。","tone":"低语","chapter":251,"line_start":139,"line_end":141},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"玉玲夫人对我们竹花帮有没有影响力？","tone":"疑问","chapter":251,"line_start":143,"line_end":143},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"幸容","listener":null,"text":"当然有哩！她对我们很支持，可是她从不插手帮务，在帮内更没有实权。故她的影响力只是来自帮中兄弟对她的尊重，遇到重大的事情时便难生作用。","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":145,"line_end":149},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"邵令周","listener":null,"text":"凌兄能否代表少帅说话。","tone":"疑问","chapter":251,"line_start":155,"line_end":157},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"当然可以！否则少帅就不会派我随桂堂主回来。","tone":"淡然","chapter":251,"line_start":159,"line_end":159},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"邵令周","listener":null,"text":"好！请凌兄立即随邵某到总管府见大王，他要和能代表寇少帅的人说话。","tone":"认真","chapter":251,"line_start":161,"line_end":163},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"邵令周","listener":null,"text":"两位堂主不用随行，有老夫和沈老便成啦！","tone":"严肃","chapter":251,"line_start":165,"line_end":167},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"长林兄竟可以这么快回来？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":251,"line_start":169,"line_end":171},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"陈长林","listener":null,"text":"轻舟顺流，到东海不过大半天，回程时顺风，也不过费了一晚多几个时辰。长林幸而不负所托，千五江南子弟兵，今晚即可抵梁都，他们用的都是自备的兵器。","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":173,"line_end":177},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"虚行之","listener":null,"text":"全是江南各大铁器老字号打制，要冒充都冒充不来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":179,"line_end":181},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"如此就更好，今次我们只是要离间敌人，而不是真的去攻击老杜的江淮军，有甚么方法可既不会损折我方的人，偏又可撩起老杜的误会和怒火呢？","tone":"欣喜","chapter":251,"line_start":183,"line_end":185},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"虚行之","listener":null,"text":"详细计划，虽待听得其飞的情报方可定细节。但最好是能在某一特别的形势下，刺杀杜伏威旗下某一重要的爱将，不论成功与否，都不愁他们不引起猜疑，进而翻脸大动干戈。","tone":"从容","chapter":251,"line_start":187,"line_end":191},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"陈长林","listener":null,"text":"甚么特别形势？","tone":"疑问","chapter":251,"line_start":193,"line_end":193},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"虚行之","listener":null,"text":"现在杜沈两军是轮流攻打江都扬州，可以想像无论是谁攻城，必是全力以赴，希望能先入城饮那口头啖汤，其中两方面自有协议。据江都来的消息说，上一次刚好是沈军攻城，攻守双方均损折甚钜，待江淮军再攻城时，便极有破城的可能，我们需要的，正是这种形势。","tone":"解释","chapter":251,"line_start":195,"line_end":199}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xu_zi_ling","name":"徐子陵","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_kou_zhong","name":"寇仲","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_xing_rong","name":"幸容","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_shao_ling_zhou","name":"邵令周","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_su_su","name":"素素","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_luo_feng","name":"骆奉","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_gui_xi_liang","name":"桂锡良","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_luo_qi_fei","name":"洛其飞","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_ling_feng","name":"凌封","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_li_zi_tong","name":"李子通","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_du_fu_wei","name":"杜伏威","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_shen_lun","name":"沈纶","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_shen_bei_chang","name":"沈北昌","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_chen_chang_lin","name":"陈长林","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_xu_xing_zhi","name":"虚行之","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_zhu_hua_bang","name":"竹花帮","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"faction_shao_shuai_jun","name":"少帅军","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"faction_ba_ling_bang","name":"巴陵帮","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]}],"locations":[{"id":"loc_yang_zhou","name":"扬州","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"loc_jiang_du","name":"江都","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"loc_yi_zhou","name":"益州","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"loc_si_chuan_shu_jun","name":"四川蜀郡","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"loc_zhong_li","name":"钟离","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":1,"line_end":199,"text":"出现在第251章"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":201,"line_end":241,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"此计妙绝，正好提供了沈纶破坏合作的动机，就是怕江淮军先一步入城，尽收胜利成果。","tone":"激动","chapter":251,"line_start":201,"line_end":203},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"虚行之","listener":null,"text":"现在我们唯一要解决的问题，就是如何避过杜沈两军，甚至李子通的耳目，因为这样浩浩荡荡的出动过千人，行上极难保密。","tone":"认真","chapter":251,"line_start":207,"line_end":209},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"原本没有可能的事，现在却变得大有可能。哈！救星来啦！","tone":"大笑","chapter":251,"line_start":211,"line_end":213},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"卜天志","listener":null,"text":"此事可包在我身上，我和各个码头的龙头大哥多少都有点交情，只要长林的人扮作我的手下，我可分批把他们送至江都附近我们一个秘巢内，等待行动的良机。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":251,"line_start":215,"line_end":217},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"虚行之","listener":null,"text":"那就万事俱备，只欠情报这东风了。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":251,"line_start":219,"line_end":219},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"不若我们把行刺的对象改为老杜本人，不是更一针到肉吗？","tone":"认真","chapter":251,"line_start":221,"line_end":223},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"陈长林","listener":null,"text":"假设杜伏威真的中计反击沈纶，我们又如何利用这情势？","tone":"疑问","chapter":251,"line_start":225,"line_end":227},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"虚行之","listener":null,"text":"杜伏威的实力远胜沈纶，必可予沈纶军士沉重的打击，那时沈纶只有循江南运河退返毗陵一途，我们可于运河上截击沈纶，攻他一个猝不及防，莫知所措。","tone":"陈述","chapter":251,"line_start":229,"line_end":231},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"此事可行吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":251,"line_start":233,"line_end":233},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"卜天志","listener":null,"text":"对江南的分歧水道，我们了若指掌，可保证当我们的战船突然于运河出现时，江南军始如梦初醒，只要我们能抢上沈纶的帅船，长林兄将可手刃沈纶。","tone":"自信","chapter":251,"line_start":235,"line_end":237},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"事不宜迟，我们立即进行准备的工夫，到时我会亲自陪长林兄上船拜会沈纶那小子，看看老天爷是否肯主持公道。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":251,"line_start":239,"line_end":241}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_kou_zhong","name":"寇仲","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":201,"line_end":241,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_xu_xing_zhi","name":"虚行之","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":201,"line_end":241,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_bu_tian_zhi","name":"卜天志","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":201,"line_end":241,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_chen_chang_lin","name":"陈长林","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":201,"line_end":241,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_shen_lun","name":"沈纶","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":201,"line_end":241,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"char_du_fu_wei","name":"杜伏威","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":201,"line_end":241,"text":"出现在第251章"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_jiang_du","name":"江都","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":201,"line_end":241,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"loc_pi_ling","name":"毗陵","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":201,"line_end":241,"text":"出现在第251章"}]},{"id":"loc_jiang_nan_yun_he","name":"江南运河","source_refs":[{"chapter":251,"line_start":201,"line_end":241,"text":"出现在第251章"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}